"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641038000,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"HWGZtuuwk2dfXx0_tq2bot9IfXEZwMCIi90eacJyEqw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x96A7d6a6b211F9D835E133b3E290Eb1a0186B36C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jGE17b0Xzax-LJnDVLRo1ZyeP1HQExB5luMGZSpbtnc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RMlcpljoAQJKufR0gHBBy5cDPCPaiCZdZYOxsGsTq7k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"cgDFOZ-AiQ6eOrUwCYtzqsJ7MNrs2tdo26T-R0HFp8e39h8ANgd_ray2XND9Za5rL94NqS3KFVm4qCTUJ8Lreg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x4d4b695a22b6785582bc2f50f5d2c719b51e861b5ef4816a2f73316bd1d35f1f391292cf8521c7d73790eefdc33055698a2fb4014a5a133fb36cfc7eee9345d21c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"jGE17b0Xzax-LJnDVLRo1ZyeP1HQExB5luMGZSpbtnc\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"RMlcpljoAQJKufR0gHBBy5cDPCPaiCZdZYOxsGsTq7k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi